.Dd October 22, 2006
.Dt VMEM_DESTROY 9
.Os
.\" ------------------------------------------------------------
.Sh NAME
.Nm vmem_create
.Nd Destroy a vmem arena
.\" ------------------------------------------------------------
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In sys/vmem.h
.\" - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
.Ft void
.Fn vmem_destroy \
"vmem_t *vm"
.\" ------------------------------------------------------------
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn vmem_destroy
destroys a vmem arena.
.Pp
.Bl -tag -width vm
.It Fa vm
The vmem arena being destroyed.
The caller should ensure that no one will use it anymore.
.El
